---
title: Diagram Sekuens — Alur Klasifikasi AI dan Penyimpanan Laporan
---
sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 👤 Masyarakat
    participant CRS as CreateReportScreen
    participant LS as LocationService
    participant AI as OnDeviceAIService
    participant ORT as ONNX Runtime\n(mambaout_tiny.onnx)
    participant ARR as AiResultReviewScreen
    participant RE as ClassificationRoutingEngine
    participant DB as LocalDatabaseService

    User->>CRS: Ambil foto (kamera/galeri)
    CRS->>LS: getCurrentLocation()
    LS-->>CRS: {latitude, longitude}

    CRS->>AI: classify(imagePath)
    activate AI
    AI->>AI: loadModel() [jika belum dimuat]
    AI->>AI: preprocessImage()\n resize → crop → normalize → tensor
    AI->>ORT: run(input_tensor)
    activate ORT
    ORT-->>AI: logits[7]
    deactivate ORT
    AI->>AI: softmax(logits)\nidentifikasi top-k predictions
    AI->>AI: mapRawLabel → IssueCategory\n(via metadata.json)
    AI-->>CRS: AiPrediction {category, confidence, rawPayload}
    deactivate AI

    CRS->>ARR: navigate(AiPrediction, location, imagePath)
    activate ARR

    ARR->>RE: buildRoutingGuidance(AiPrediction)
    activate RE
    RE->>RE: normalizeRawLabel()\npetakan ke RoutingCluster
    RE-->>ARR: ClassificationRoutingGuidance\n{cluster, operationalLabel, agencies}
    deactivate RE

    ARR-->>User: Tampilkan:\n• Kategori + confidence\n• Top predictions\n• Rekomendasi instansi
    User->>ARR: Konfirmasi / Koreksi kategori

    ARR->>DB: saveReport(Report)
    activate DB
    DB-->>ARR: reportId
    deactivate DB
    deactivate ARR

    ARR-->>User: Laporan tersimpan ✓
